    General Stores in Vile Parle West, Mumbai

    (3530 Ratings & Reviews) 4.0 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Vile Parle West, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Vile Parle West, Mumbai from the list given above.
